  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Pyre Hounds are hunters. They circle prey, use Blazing Pounce when the angle is right, and pursue routed enemies without needing instruction to do so. Against a single target they are relentless; a Summoner who calls one to chase something down and keep it occupied will find it performs that task until one of them stops burning. A Cooperative Pyre Hound guarding a location patrols intelligently, using its Keen Smell to detect approach before anything is visible.</p>"
